                     <interp inst="t18510616-1299-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>stealing 3 pieces of cloth, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18510616-name-223" type="victimName">
